item.description:
Public hearing and meeting to receive public input on Strafford County Commissioners 2011 proposed Budget. To be held at Superior Courtroom I, Justice and Administration Building. Snow date is Wednesday February 2nd at 7pm same location.
This is your opporitunity to voice your concerns, questions and opinions regarding the County Budget. Remember that the top 2 leadership positions were lost through treachery by Julie Brown who sits on the delegation.
item.name: Strafford County Delegation Proposed Budget Hearing and Meeting
